Package: PhDChapter3
Title: Scale-Dependent Beta Diversity Utilities for PhD Chapter 3
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Rahil", family = "Amin", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Utilities to retrieve species occurrences (ALA), snap to grids,
    generate variable-resolution hexagonal grids, and compute beta-diversity
    across spatial scales for ecological analysis.
